      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff00cc&gt;Mitic&lt;/FONT&gt;, down boy!&amp;nbsp; ;)&amp;nbsp; I'm not suggesting an FV ruleset, and this server will have a unique ruleset no matter what.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;I'm just suggesting we take the shared bank out of the equation for launch.&amp;nbsp; This server is guaranteed to have a bunch of peeps gaming the system any way they can to 'win' the server.&amp;nbsp; (&lt;EM&gt;Very&lt;/EM&gt; dubious achievement considering the whole game has been "spoiled" already, but that's another story).&amp;nbsp; The shared bank makes it too easy and &lt;U&gt;hurts the hard work, community&amp;nbsp;and immersion&lt;/U&gt; that 9,999 threads on this board have attributed the original appeal of the game to.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;I can guess why the shared bank is in the game now, at least from Sony's perspective&amp;nbsp;-- it cuts customer service cost for folks who lost stuff doing drop-pass or PC-pass.&amp;nbsp; If you allow multiple toons per account you reintroduce the customer service headache for PC-passes loss... I doubt the code is still around to re-introduce drop-passes.&amp;nbsp; Best to limit the # of toons per account initially and give the community a chance to florish.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
